<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &quot;Yoo hab me wurd dat it be gived back,&quot; the large shadowknight vowed as he held out a hand.<br>
<br>
&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &quot;I do not expect you to understand,&quot; Talastius's voice was low and menacing, meant for Brynvin alone to hear as he placed the pouch into the ogre's large, calloused palm, &quot;but I will not soon forget that.&quot;  Her jaw setting firmly in place at the mild threat, unwilling to pursue the matter futher just yet, Brynvin turned away from him and cleared her throat.<br>
